{"id": "1267377858586742795", "channel_id": "1267377858586742795", "type": 0, "author_id": "1188482378948165682", "author_name": "phantom_ye", "author_bot": false, "content": "1.环娜的档案有两行是多打了回车？在这里分行很莫名其妙诶（有逗号那两行）\n2.汀克特的档案最后两行，感觉应该写在菲茵特的档案内，或者把“妹妹”改为“姐姐”\n3.菲茵特的档案内“在某个灾难发生后，赚来了唯一一张机票，将菲茵特哄骗上了离开荒芜行星的航程”这一段建议加上主语“汀克特”或者“妹妹”\n暂时先看到这里有后续我会在评论区补充", "timestamp": "2024-07-29T07:07:08.229000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-07-29T09:10:27.391000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 16}], "attachments": [{"id": "1267377858947584042", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-07-29-15-01-59-210_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 104187, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1267377858586742795/1267377858947584042/Screenshot_2024-07-29-15-01-59-210_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69cc1b5c&is=69cac9dc&hm=a3c18c8e4c92a5504705cd01eed27c86825190f7b0dc3a32f2de0e706a47b0ec&"}, {"id": "1267377859324936213", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-07-29-15-00-08-319_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 98242, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1267377858586742795/1267377859324936213/Screenshot_2024-07-29-15-00-08-319_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69cc1b5c&is=69cac9dc&hm=74528ca97e22ed2c088c296adbc392efb3af3c4ba0b72cf96364208629447cc6&"}, {"id": "1267377859564015717", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-07-29-15-00-54-258_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 107227, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1267377858586742795/1267377859564015717/Screenshot_2024-07-29-15-00-54-258_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69cc1b5c&is=69cac9dc&hm=2e19070e5776a2f2e197036a765759334ef5d9e5b2cd87880f163ee6435d9520&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1267377858586742795", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「處理中」游戏内文案的一点修改意见", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1181168158