{"id": "1267381857960329246", "channel_id": "1267377858586742795", "type": 0, "author_id": "1188482378948165682", "author_name": "phantom_ye", "author_bot": false, "content": "6.莉莉档案和剧情表现严重不符。（1）弗朗西斯原本对融蚀没什么了解，她只是能够看到。（2）莉莉是被意外唤醒的，主线里明确写了这一点。（3）弗朗西斯不知道唤醒体莉莉就是她的女儿，主线中有母女相认的情节。", "timestamp": "2024-07-29T07:23:01.754000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1267381857708675143", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-07-29-15-20-19-878_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 101048, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1267377858586742795/1267381857708675143/Screenshot_2024-07-29-15-20-19-878_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69cc1f15&is=69cacd95&hm=7a7efdef07f4b393ddc55c28dab11dc7a01d55fbc4518d34600a9c89f5a5183e&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1267377858586742795", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「處理中」游戏内文案的一点修改意见", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1181168158678204497"]}
