{"id": "1267370007965208576", "channel_id": "1267368287239540747", "type": 0, "author_id": "1155911864346218627", "author_name": "ventus1017_30730", "author_bot": false, "content": "2. 汀克特\n據角色檔案，汀克特與菲茵特為孿生姐妹。其中菲茵特是姐姐，汀克特是妹妹。\n在最新實裝的汀克特檔案中稱謂出現了錯誤。不過菲茵特的檔案是正確的。", "timestamp": "2024-07-29T06:35:56.495000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1267370007382458452", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-07-29-16-32-53-402_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 104608, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1267368287239540747/1267370007382458452/Screenshot_2024-07-29-16-32-53-402_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69cc140c&is=69cac28c&hm=4e7fc175fd992feb8bccaef8f491941751623c528732bc2bbcdc5b18f4901208&"}, {"id": "1267370007717871647", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-07-29-16-33-08-405_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 113006, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1267368287239540747/1267370007717871647/Screenshot_2024-07-29-16-33-08-405_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69cc140c&is=69cac28c&hm=8f02cf7f5b63b6562eb0d7b47e0b8be36d83409449d2586938322f5df276dc64&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1267368287239540747", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "關於新實裝的角色檔案中出現的文本錯誤", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
